                     <interp inst="t18210214-39-person506" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner leave the counter, go to a glass-case, take a book out, and put it into his pocket.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
